## Typography

No fonts were specified by the client. The following pairing is recommended based on the brand personality (professional, industrial, trustworthy).

### Heading font: Montserrat

Strong, geometric sans-serif with a modern industrial feel. Communicates confidence and authority. Widely used in B2B and industrial sectors.

### Body font: Open Sans

Clean, highly readable sans-serif that pairs well with Montserrat. Neutral enough to let the content speak while maintaining professionalism. Excellent at small sizes for body copy, captions, and form fields.

|Element              |Font      |Weight        |Size           |
|---------------------|----------|--------------|---------------|
|H1 — Page Titles     |Montserrat|Bold (700)    |42-48px        |
|H2 — Section Headings|Montserrat|SemiBold (600)|30-36px        |
|H3 — Sub-sections    |Montserrat|SemiBold (600)|22-26px        |
|H4 — Card Titles     |Montserrat|Medium (500)  |18-20px        |
|Body Text            |Open Sans |Regular (400) |16-18px        |
|Small / Captions     |Open Sans |Regular (400) |14px           |
|Buttons / CTAs       |Montserrat|SemiBold (600)|16px, uppercase|
|Nav Links            |Open Sans |SemiBold (600)|15-16px        |

**[INFERRED]** — No fonts provided by client. Needs approval.

