## Logo usage

The client provided a branding identity PDF (“Penguin Trailers Identity 3.pdf”), a PNG logo, and a logo proof PDF. The logo features a penguin icon alongside the “Penguin Trailers” wordmark.

### Recommended usage

- **Header:** Full logo (icon + wordmark), horizontally arranged, on white or light background.
- **Footer:** Reversed logo (white) on dark navy background.
- **Favicon / Mobile:** Penguin icon only, simplified.
- **Minimum clear space:** Equal to the height of the penguin icon on all sides.

